  "dialogue": {
    "0": {
      "id": "0",
      "speaker": "Dame Guisarme",
      "text": "From one warrior to another, I must say, it's just embarrassing the way the Flaming Fist lets this murderer go around killing people and getting away with it.",
      "context": "InternalNodeContext: The base topic of this character. You can choose between: Murders at temple, Steel Watch, Brain-Quakes, Impending coronation of Gortash, Gang war: Guild vs. Stone Men, Approaching Army of the Absolute",
      "checkflags": [
        "LOW_Elfsong_HasmetPatron001 = False"
      ],
      "setflags": [
        "LOW_Elfsong_HasmetPatron001"
      ],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "3",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "10": {
          "id": "10",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "You don't think the Fists are up to the task?",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "3",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "5": {
              "id": "5",
              "speaker": "Dame Guisarme",
              "text": "Oh, they used to be capable enough, but they've gotten slow and lazy. Corruption makes you soft.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "3",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "15": {
                  "id": "15",
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "You think the Flaming Fist have had their day? They might be interested to hear that.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "3",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "4": {
                      "id": "4",
                      "speaker": "Dame Guisarme",
                      "text": "Oh, knock it off. You're no friend of the Fists, I can tell just by looking at you. You're more my type. Independent.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "17": {
                          "id": "17",
                          "speaker": "Dame Guisarme",
                          "text": "No, those soft lads will never crack this case the way they're going.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "6": {
                              "id": "6",
                              "speaker": "Dame Guisarme",
                              "text": "And when they fail - and they will, count on it - the Flaming Fists know where to find Dame Guisarme. And then it will be my turn.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": true,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {}
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                },
                "12": {
                  "id": "12",
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "How would you deal with it?",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "3",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "16": {
                      "id": "16",
                      "speaker": "Dame Guisarme",
                      "text": "I'd start a special crime unit, a half dozen hard cases, grab some likely losers in the back alleys, and beat on them until we got some answers.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "3",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "7": {
          "id": "7",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "The Fists are only good for handling riots. Investigation isn't their strong suit.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [
            "Wyll -1",
            "Karlach 1",
            "Jaheira 1",
            "Minsc 1"
          ],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "12",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "11": {
              "id": "11",
              "speaker": "Dame Guisarme",
              "text": "You don't need subtlety to sort these matters out, just persistence. That's what I told Commander Portyr, anyway.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "12",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "14": {
                  "id": "14",
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "What did the Fist commander have to say to that?",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "3": {
                      "id": "3",
                      "speaker": "Dame Guisarme",
                      "text": "Commander Portyr says she already has some 'investigators' she trusts. Soft-talking namby-pambies, I'd wager.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "9": {
                          "id": "9",
                          "speaker": "Dame Guisarme",
                          "text": "But when they fail - and they will, count on it - she knows where to find Dame Guisarme. And then it will be my turn.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": true,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {}
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "8": {
          "id": "8",
          "speaker": "Player",
          "text": "Leave.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "",
